Convert::Recode is a front end to the GNU recode program.  It will
build a perl tr/// function based on the mapping tables that recode
knows about.

  use Convert::Recode qw(ebcdic_to_ascii);
  while (<>) {
     print ebcdic_to_ascii($_);
  }

